Niger Gets 25 Million-Euros Grant From EU to Reduce Poverty, Meet Goals

-- B y   D j i b r i l   S a i d o u
-- 
2011-07-19T15:54:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/niger-gets-25-million-euros-grant-from-eu-to-reduce-poverty-meet-goals.html
The European Union will give Niger a
25 million-euro grant to help the country reduce poverty and
meet the Millennium Development Goals, said Andris Piebalgs, the
European Commissioner for Development.  “This payment embodies the full resumption of our
cooperation with Niger,” Piebalgs said in an e-mailed statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
